dialog.mdl-dialog.mdl-shadow--2dp(id='consent-info')
  h4.mdl-dialog__title Obtaining Consent
  .mdl-dialog__content
    p.
      Research studies that involve human subjects typically require some form of ethics
      review. Depending on the country, this may be review by an institutional review
      board (IRB), or by an ethics committee (EC). For some studies, consent may be required
      to conduct a research study, which means that the researcher must ensure that each
      participant is fully informed about the nature of the study, and must obtain a signed
      consent from each participant. Additionally, consent may be required as a condition
      of app review.
    p See the #[a(href='http://researchkit.org/docs/docs/InformedConsent/InformedConsent.html', target='_blank') ResearchKit guide] #[i.material-icons(style='font-size: 1em') launch] for further information.
    .mdl-dialog__actions
      button.mdl-button.mdl-button--colored.mdl-js-button.close(type='button') OK
script dialogPolyfill.registerDialog(document.getElementbyId('consent-info'));
